  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "人気のサンリオキャラクター「キティちゃん」が、中国の「易経」を使って占いを行います。キティはミニゲームをプレイし、占いをすることでレベルが上がり、占える内容が増えていきます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A Hello Kitty game for the Game Boy Color.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The game includes two main modes, Read Fortune and Study. When playing the game, the player can enter their details such as full name and date of birth. The Read Fortune mode features an elaborate fortune telling system for oneself or a friend.\n\nThe Study mode allows the player to play various minigames, including a game where the player has to flip cards with certain runes on them and avoid matching the rune shown on the left hand side of the screen and another in which the player has to jump across stepping stones without falling in the water.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
